reviews.text: It was actually my second time being here, and the foods are delicious. The first time I had a good impression, the second time, I think I would come for more. Gotta try their fish skin dumping, it is amazing.
Afternoon tea taste good with fair price
Even their lormie is delicious, but we took a long time to be served, more than 30 minutes waited 👎 and the servant did'nt told us.
The food quality is very good and delicious.

There are not many Fujian restaurants in Hong Kong. Putien is one which signifies the modernized Fujian crusine. The place is clean and the food tastes good overall. The menu has a lot selections with pictures showing what each dish looks like. My favorite is the dessert - the taro paste which comes with the set.
